    "It allows systems to adapt based on prior exchanges and the established context.",
    "In this method, the dialogue system navigates through various predefined states based on user inputs and context.",
    "The transitions between these states are determined by rules, ensuring the conversation progresses logically and coherently. 3.",
    "Computational argumentation: Grounded in argumentative principles, this strategy frames conversations as dialogue games.",
    "Participants adhere to a set of rules, enabling structured arguments and counterarguments to develop. 4."
